  <brief_title>Local Infiltration Analgesia vs Adductor Canal Block for Analgesia After Anterior Cruciate Ligament Reconstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Postoperative Analgesic Efficacy of Local Infiltration Analgesia Versus Adductor Canal Block After Anterior Cruciate Ligament Reconstruction: A Randomised Controlled Double-blinded Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
