  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients from 18 to 50 years old scheduled to undergo anterior cruciate ligament
             reconstruction

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  peripheral neuropathy

          -  pre-existing femoral neuropathy

          -  diabetes mellitus

          -  alcoholism

          -  drug addiction

          -  cancer with chemotherapy

          -  chronic pain state
      </textblock>
